      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PUSR   10        ﾏｰﾅﾞｰxb
     C                     PARM           PSHN1   5        ﾍ]ﾌﾞ] 1
     C                     PARM           PSHN2   5        ﾍ]ﾌﾞ] 2
     C                     PARM           PSHN3   2        ﾍ]ﾌﾞ] 3
